.work/
# Rust workspace build output (engine/ + tui/). Source manifests and the root Cargo.lock are
# tracked; Cargo resolves every member into this shared target/ tree.
/target/
# Old standalone build directories may remain on a developer machine after the workspace move;
# they are caches only and must not become source changes.
engine/target/
tui/target/
# Stray stdout/stderr capture artifacts occasionally left behind by ad hoc test/debug
# runs of tests/launchers/*.ps1 (e.g. manual out/err redirection while iterating).
tests/launchers/*.tmp
